{"title":"game","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":["高斯消元"],"operation":{"submit":"https://loj.ac/problem/6357#submit_code","submissions":"https://loj.ac/submissions?problem_id=6357","statistics":"https://loj.ac/problem/6357/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://loj.ac/problem/6357/testdata","discussion":"https://loj.ac/discussion/problem/6357"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$n$ 个人逆时针排成一个环，从编号为 $1$ 的人开始逆时针从 $1$ 至 $k$ 报数，报到 $k$ 的人有 $\\frac{1}{2}$ 的概率出局。无论其出局与否，下一个人报 $1$。\r\n\r\n求编号为 $1$ 的人最后存活的概率。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"只有一行，两个整数 $n, k$。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"求编号为 $1$ 的人最后存活的概率对 $10^9+7$ 取模后的值。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```plain\r\n2 1\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```plain\r\n333333336\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例解释\r\n$$\\frac{1}{4} + \\frac{1}{16} + \\frac{1}{64} + \\frac{1}{256} + \\cdots = \\frac{1}{3}$$"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于 $100\\%$ 的数据，$n \\le 2000,k \\le 10^9$"}]}